te-water and effluent treatment, and other engineering solutions; and lubricants, such as rust preventives, cutting oils, wire-drawing lubricants, heat treatment fluid, forming fluid \u0096 non wire, industrial cleaner, and other industrial oil. In addition, the company is involved in the conceptualization, designing, manufacturing, and installing of surface finishing systems; and operates shopping malls. The company serves its products to automotive and heavy equipment, hardware, electronics, white goods, jewelry, PSUs, aeronautics, railway, defense, oil and gas, marine, drinking water, OEM, power, chemical and fertilizer, hardware and fasteners, steel, electricals and electronics, architectural and bath fittings, general manufacturing, wire and cables, tube and pipe, die casting, bearings, tool and auto manufacturing, aluminum, and glass industries. Grauer & Weil (India) Limited was incorporated in 1957 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}